   <S PAR='23' RSNT='1' SNO='23'>PREFACE</S>
   <S PAR='24' RSNT='1' SNO='24'>The Ministry of God s Word contains eighteen lessons given by Watchman Nee to his co-workers in a training at Kuling between 1948 and 1949.</S>
   <S PAR='25' RSNT='1' SNO='25'>The chapters are divided into four sections.</S>
   <S PAR='26' RSNT='1' SNO='26'>The main subject is the ministers of God s word and their ministry.</S>
   <S PAR='27' RSNT='1' SNO='27'>The structure and divisions of the book are well organized, and the content is rich and unique.</S>
   <S PAR='28' RSNT='1' SNO='28'>May the Lord bless the reader with the light and revelation contained in these pages.</S>
